{"tid":2356791,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全球左膠群魔亂舞 法加英歐聲援拜登 稱暴力不會推翻拜登勝出的結果","createTime":"2021-01-07T04:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T05:09:21.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2f355fb20703108b51462f559203768b609181f2","tid":2356791,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"馬克龍斥美國會衝突 杜魯多稱暴力不會推翻人民意願<br />\n<br />\n多國領袖譴責美國國會山莊的衝突。法國總統馬克龍在Twitter以英語及法語發布影片，批評今次的衝突，形容發動今次襲擊的不代表美國人，他相信美國作為民主國家的力量，並向美國表達支持。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大總理杜魯多對美國民主的襲擊深感不安和悲傷，形容暴力永遠不會成功推翻人民的意願。<br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜表示，美國國會的衝突場面可恥，形容美國代表著世界的民主，現時應該要和平有序進行權力移交。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲理事會主席米歇爾在Twitter貼文說，美國國會的場面令人震驚，有信心美國可以確保和平將權力移交至在大選中勝選、民主黨的拜登手上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569113-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569113-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5qix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=e9dbc10c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569113-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0484a2d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569113-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5cbf6635300d02c7c635395c1959eb083bf9a0fc","tid":2356791,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:25:09.000Z","msg":"下個揸旗一定係新威權主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88b3fabebb4b4a311cdecfaa3d9a693750bb687","tid":2356791,"uid":249979,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:45:27.000Z","msg":"權力令人腐敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16acb2f70af49dcf18bca5a4b2581d23c2cfb05","tid":2356791,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5cbf6635300d02c7c635395c1959eb083bf9a0fc","tid":2356791,"uid":60434,"like":0,"